#summary Benchmark results for Q9400 Vista 64
#labels Deprecated

There are a few changes in this benchmark since the last one.  
  * If possible, all memory was predeclared and the time involved in predeclaring was not counted.
  * Commons-math, EJML, Parallel-Colt and all were upgraded.
  * Plots are now relative to the medium value of each test.
  * MTJ and Colt/Parallel-Colt benchmarks were changed since several operations modified their inputs.

Links to the results:
  * [#Basic_Operation_Results Basic Operations]
  * [#Solving_Linear_Systems Solving Linear Systems]
  * [#Matrix_Decompositions Matrix Decompositions]
